title: Kraftig rentekutt fra Russlands sentralbank
cleaned_sentences: Powerful interest cut from Russia's central bank February 28, Bank of Russia raised interest rates by 10.5 percentage points.
Nearly five months later, the interest rate is well below the level from when Russia invaded Ukraine.
At lunchtime on Friday, Russia's central bank cuts interest rates by 1.50 percentage points to 8.0 per cent.
